OL,7,FOfficers said they had arrested a 50-
OL,8,Fyear-old man from Dudley on Tuesday (6
OL,9,FFebruary).
OL,11,FHe was taken into custody and
OL,12,Fquestioned on suspicion of a racially
OL,13,Faggravated public order offence.
OL,15,FBut, the man has since been bailed
OL,16,Fwith strict conditions - which
OL,17,Fincludes not being able to attend any
OL,18,Ffootball game in the UK - while police
OL,19,Fenquiries continue.
