OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "The club
OL,8,Fcontinues to offer its full support to
OL,9,FWest Midlands Police's criminal
OL,10,Finvestigation of this matter and
OL,11,Fremains in contact with Birmingham
OL,12,FCity to ensure Juninho Bacuna receives
OL,13,Fthe support he requires.
OL,15,F"The club takes a strong stance
OL,16,Fagainst all forms of discrimination
OL,17,Fand will do all it can to ensure
OL,18,Fanyone found guilty of racism faces
OL,19,Fthe toughest available legal
OL,20,Fpunishment, in addition to a lifetime
OL,21,Fban from The Hawthorns."
